{"page_content": "本次更新覆盖账号日志、访问审批与导出留痕三个场景，目的是让员工知道哪些操作会被记录以及记录保存多久。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_privacy_notice", "title": "员工隐私告知更新说明", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/privacy-notice-refresh", "published_at": "2025-01-12", "format": "html", "authority_type": "policy", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "员工隐私告知更新说明", "section_order": 1}}
{"page_content": "所有访问客户数据、员工数据或内部审计看板的人员都在适用范围内，包含正式员工、外包同事与临时支援账号。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_privacy_notice", "title": "员工隐私告知更新说明", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/privacy-notice-refresh", "published_at": "2025-01-12", "format": "html", "authority_type": "policy", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "适用范围", "section_order": 2}}
{"page_content": "访问审批记录需要保留申请人、审批人、审批时间、访问原因和关闭时间，便于后续做证据追踪。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_privacy_notice", "title": "员工隐私告知更新说明", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/privacy-notice-refresh", "published_at": "2025-01-12", "format": "html", "authority_type": "policy", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "记录要求", "section_order": 3}}
{"page_content": "临时访问权限在开通后必须进入复核队列，避免长期残留的高权限账号继续保留。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_access_review", "title": "临时访问复核流程", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/access-review-playbook", "published_at": "2025-02-03", "format": "html", "authority_type": "process", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "临时访问复核流程", "section_order": 1}}
{"page_content": "开通后 24 小时内完成第一次复核，超过 7 天仍未关闭的访问申请需要升级到数据治理负责人。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_access_review", "title": "临时访问复核流程", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/access-review-playbook", "published_at": "2025-02-03", "format": "html", "authority_type": "process", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "复核时点", "section_order": 2}}
{"page_content": "复核时至少检查工单编号、审批链、访问对象、导出动作和关闭结果，必要时补充截图与审计日志。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_access_review", "title": "临时访问复核流程", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/access-review-playbook", "published_at": "2025-02-03", "format": "html", "authority_type": "process", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "复核证据", "section_order": 3}}
{"page_content": "供应商接入前要先补齐用途说明、数据范围和保存期限，避免后续评估时只剩口头解释。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_vendor_faq", "title": "第三方安全评估 FAQ", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/vendor-assessment-faq", "published_at": "2024-11-08", "format": "html", "authority_type": "faq", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "第三方安全评估 FAQ", "section_order": 1}}
{"page_content": "一旦供应商新增高敏感字段处理、跨境传输或新的子处理者，就必须重新触发评估。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_vendor_faq", "title": "第三方安全评估 FAQ", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/vendor-assessment-faq", "published_at": "2024-11-08", "format": "html", "authority_type": "faq", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "什么时候必须复评", "section_order": 2}}
{"page_content": "评估材料至少包括问卷、整改结论、负责人审批和上线前确认记录。", "metadata": {"source_id": "web_vendor_faq", "title": "第三方安全评估 FAQ", "source_ref": "https://intranet.example.local/vendor-assessment-faq", "published_at": "2024-11-08", "format": "html", "authority_type": "faq", "parser_used": "trafilatura+beautifulsoup", "section_heading": "最低交付物", "section_order": 3}}
{"page_content": "DSAR 工单进入队列后，第一步不是直接回复，而是先验证申请人与数据主体的关系。", "metadata": {"source_id": "md_dsar_handbook", "title": "DSAR 响应手册", "source_ref": "internal://privacy/dsar-handbook", "published_at": "2025-02-20", "format": "md", "authority_type": "playbook", "parser_used": "markdown-normalizer", "section_heading": "DSAR 响应手册", "section_order": 1}}
{"page_content": "需要确认工单编号、身份材料和申请范围。 如果申请内容涉及历史导出记录，还要补拉审计日志。", "metadata": {"source_id": "md_dsar_handbook", "title": "DSAR 响应手册", "source_ref": "internal://privacy/dsar-handbook", "published_at": "2025-02-20", "format": "md", "authority_type": "playbook", "parser_used": "markdown-normalizer", "section_heading": "核验要求", "section_order": 2}}
{"page_content": "标准响应时限是 30 天。遇到材料不完整或范围不清楚时，要先发澄清通知，再重新计算内部处理计划。", "metadata": {"source_id": "md_dsar_handbook", "title": "DSAR 响应手册", "source_ref": "internal://privacy/dsar-handbook", "published_at": "2025-02-20", "format": "md", "authority_type": "playbook", "parser_used": "markdown-normalizer", "section_heading": "时限管理", "section_order": 3}}
{"page_content": "跨境传输例外检查清单 1. 确认传输是否属于紧急响应、履约必要或数据主体单独同意。 2. 记录接收方、字段范围、保留期限和补救措施。 3. 若例外理由无法形成书面证据，则不能直接放行。", "metadata": {"source_id": "txt_transfer_checklist", "title": "跨境传输例外检查清单", "source_ref": "internal://privacy/transfer-exception-checklist", "published_at": "2024-12-18", "format": "txt", "authority_type": "checklist", "parser_used": "plain-text-loader", "section_heading": "正文", "section_order": 1}}
{"page_content": "访问审批日志至少保留 180 天，便于后续事件追踪和复盘。", "metadata": {"source_id": "pdf_retention_schedule", "title": "数据保留与删除时限表", "source_ref": "internal://privacy/retention-schedule", "published_at": "2025-01-30", "format": "pdf", "authority_type": "schedule", "parser_used": "mineru-cache", "section_heading": "1. 保留范围", "section_order": 1, "page": 1}}
{"page_content": "临时导出文件应在业务完成后 30 天内删除，除非存在监管调查要求；如果进入正式调查，需要记录延期决定与责任人。", "metadata": {"source_id": "pdf_retention_schedule", "title": "数据保留与删除时限表", "source_ref": "internal://privacy/retention-schedule", "published_at": "2025-01-30", "format": "pdf", "authority_type": "schedule", "parser_used": "mineru-cache", "section_heading": "2. 删除时限", "section_order": 2, "page": 2}}
